Every bottle of wine in the assortment at Wainscott Main has been hand-selected by our sommelier. We can create an order for you based upon your personal tastes and preferences. Set a budget here and enjoy the same personal shopping experience our in-store customers have come to count on.

Let us know at checkout what your favorite producers, regions and grape varietals are and we will tailor your delivery to your specifications. WMW&S draws from the broadest assortment of suppliers on the East End, offering many wines exclusively, including 60+ different rosés from all over the world.

Minimum $75
